beer_brewer_name: Port Brewing Co / The Lost Abbey
review_blob: Not much aroma with this one but the flavor comes on strong.  The cherries are strong as expected along with dark fruits.  The strong flavor covers the alcohol niclely - 10.5% but easily drinkable.
beer_name: Lost Abbey Judgment Day - Bourbon Barrel: Cherries

review_blob: Great flavor with just enough sweetness. A little carmel and complex flavors while the alcohol stays in the background.
